WHAT I BUILT

A live RAG (Retrieval-Augmented Generation) chatbot that answers eCommerce content operations questions grounded in a 6-document knowledge base. Anyone can open the link and get accurate, standards-based answers on product descriptions, taxonomy, image compliance, content quality, terminology, and attribute extraction.

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

THE PROBLEM IT SOLVES

eCommerce content teams waste significant time answering the same questions repeatedly:
- How long should a product description be?
- Where do I classify this product?
- What images are required for this category?
- What does this term mean?

Without a knowledge system, answers are inconsistent and dependent on senior team members. This slows onboarding, creates quality variability, and burns time that should go toward higher-value work.

The AI Assistant makes the knowledge instantly accessible to anyone, anytime.

