TOOLS USED

Platform: Botpress (browser-based, no installation required)
RAG engine: Botpress built-in knowledge base with semantic search
LLM: GPT-4o (via Botpress)
Knowledge base: 6 custom plain text documents
Deployment: Cloud-hosted, shareable public link
Cost: Free tier

