THE KNOWLEDGE BASE (6 DOCUMENTS)

01 — Product Description Style Guide
Structure, tone, word counts by channel, common errors, quality checklist

02 — Product Taxonomy Guide
10 top-level categories with definitions, subcategories, classification rules for edge cases

03 — Image Compliance Checklist
Technical specs, content standards, category-specific rules, image sequence standard

04 — Content Quality Checklist
5 quality dimensions (completeness, accuracy, clarity, consistency, searchability), title formula, bullet point standards, quality tiers

05 — eCommerce Glossary
25+ terms: A+ content, attribution, dark listing, ghost mannequin, PDP, quick commerce, retail readiness, SKU, taxonomy, and more

06 — Attribute Extraction Guide
Mandatory attributes by category (Electronics, Food, Fashion, Beauty, Home), extraction process, common errors

