HOW IT WAS BUILT

Step 1: Created 6 knowledge base documents covering eCommerce content standards
Step 2: Created a Botpress account and new bot
Step 3: Uploaded all 6 documents to the Botpress knowledge base
Step 4: Configured system prompt to constrain the bot to eCommerce content topics and instruct it to ground answers in the knowledge base
Step 5: Tested with 3 questions — all answered accurately from knowledge base content
Step 6: Published and generated shareable link

Total build time: approximately 2 hours

