CHALLENGES FACED

- Flowise on Render.com exceeded the 512MB free tier memory limit during startup — build succeeded but deployment failed
- Stack AI free tier had access restrictions
- Resolved by switching to Botpress — fully browser-based, no infrastructure required, free tier sufficient for portfolio purposes

